    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 Porsche 718 Cayman that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled environment and treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating. The Jet Black Metallic exterior is flawless, devoid of any stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats retain their original matte finish and suppleness, with no wear on the bolsters and the distinct scent of a new Porsche. Every electronic component, from the PCM infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, this Cayman is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, folder-bound service history performed exclusively by authorized Porsche technicians. The most recent service included a full fluid flush and a multi-point inspection, which it passed with zero advisories. The staggered alloy wheels are pristine, without a hint of curb rash, and are wrapped in high-performance tires with near-maximum tread depth. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
